5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

sheet-event-mask

Generic function

Summary

Returns the event mask of the specified sheet.

Signature

sheet-event-mask sheet => integer

Arguments

sheet
An instance of type <sheet>.

Values

integer
An instance of type <integer>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the event mask of sheet.
